EN: Controlling impulses requires some training.

ZH: 她的冲动改变了她的生活轨迹。
EN: Her impulse changed the trajectory of her life.

ZH: 冲动通常会带来后悔。
EN: Impulsiveness often leads to regret.

ZH: 我们要尽量避免冲动购物。
EN: We should try to avoid impulsive shopping as much as possible.

ZH: 冲动的人经常后悔他们的举动。
